Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.52,0:00:14.02,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「ミニチュアローズ」によって 王と共に爆死した
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.52,0:00:14.02,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This is it. My brother sent the URL. Great! Let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.49,0:01:55.99,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}王！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.49,0:01:55.99,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}to face the Phantom Troupe \Nand avenge the Kurta, Gon and Killua also prepare for the auction
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.51,0:02:00.51,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あっ！ あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.51,0:02:00.51,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}in Yorknew City.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.57,0:02:10.49,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あぁ…！ 息がある！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.57,0:02:10.49,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This is the website for Hunters?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.01,0:02:15.99,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}だが　チクショ！ 早くしないと王が！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.01,0:02:15.99,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yeah, I've heard that Hunters \Nworldwide post information here. Worldwide?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.99,0:02:18.48,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}間に合わねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.99,0:02:18.48,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.48,0:02:30.48,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}とてもピトーまでは 王が持たねえよ！ 大丈夫　私が王を救う！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.48,0:02:30.48,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Please swipe your Hunter License, and enter your license code.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.00,0:02:44.54,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}私を召し上がっていただく。 それだけのこと。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.00,0:02:44.54,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Put the cursor on the bartender. What kind of information would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.99,0:02:48.01,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あっ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.99,0:02:48.01,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Wow! There's so much! Select the game category.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:02:58.99,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あっ…　あぁ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:02:58.99,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It will cost twenty million Jenny.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:02.56,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}さぁ　私の細胞達よ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:02.56,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Twenty million... So they won't give out the \Ninformation for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.56,0:03:07.00,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}隅々まで行きわたり　王を癒やせ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.56,0:03:07.00,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Well, we don't really have a choice. Deposit twenty million...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.00,0:04:05.50,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お　お　お…。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.00,0:04:05.50,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}One person who owned the game
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.50,0:04:07.50,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}王！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.50,0:04:07.50,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}hired fifty Hunters to give it a shot, but none of them ever came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.50,0:04:16.98,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}王。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.50,0:04:16.98,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I hear that you can return \Nif you find a save point. Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:20.98,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}いかがですか？　ご気分は。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:20.98,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This information is from \Nthe Hunter website. It's gotta be accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.01,0:04:27.01,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}えも言えぬ美味。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.01,0:04:27.01,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}At the Yorknew City auction, seven copies of Greed Island \Nwill be up for sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.53,0:04:33.48,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}楽園の空気を吸うがごとく
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.53,0:04:33.48,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The lowest starting bid is 8.9 billion Jenny.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.48,0:04:38.48,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}力が　見る見る 満ちて来るのが分かる。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.48,0:04:38.48,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}8.9 billion?! The price has shot up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.51,0:04:44.51,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まさに　妖精のミスト。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.51,0:04:44.51,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That's 3 billion more than the retail price! Difficulty of obtainment is G-rank. Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.99,0:04:48.99,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}なんと…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.99,0:04:48.99,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The game is considered a legend, but there are plenty of copies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.08,0:04:57.01,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}なんと… もったいないお言葉！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.08,0:04:57.01,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If you have enough money, \Nit's relatively easy to procure. Hmm, a G...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.01,0:04:59.51,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うっ！　うぅ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.01,0:04:59.51,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Lower than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.51,0:05:07.51,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ハァ　ハァ　ハァ…。 それは　よろしゅうございました。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.51,0:05:07.51,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The message is that if I can't \Neven get a simple game, I'll never be able to find you, Ging.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.48,0:05:15.55,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}存分にお召し上がりくださいませ。 たっぷりと用意してあります。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.48,0:05:15.55,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Still, the money is a big problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.99,0:05:19.48,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}はぁ…　あっ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.99,0:05:19.48,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Hey, can we participate in the auction?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.48,0:05:23.00,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}たまらぬ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.48,0:05:23.00,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They're starting at 8.9 billion!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.00,0:05:28.99,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}この味を…　知ってしまっては…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.00,0:05:28.99,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That's out of our league. No, I mean by selling stuff. Selling?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:32.52,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}もう…　他のものは
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:32.52,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That's it! We can look for treasure, \Nand then auction it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.52,0:05:36.02,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}食えぬではないか。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.52,0:05:36.02,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Okay! We can start with the 800 million we earned
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:39.98,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あぁ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:39.98,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}at Heavens Arena, and go from there. Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.98,0:05:49.01,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あぁ！ 王！　王！　王！　王！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.98,0:05:49.01,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}First, we'll start with online flea \Nmarkets and auction websites. And see what we can dig up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.01,0:05:57.50,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}もう　これ以上　私を 喜びの天空へと　いざなうのは おやめください！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.01,0:05:57.50,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We'll increase our money, \Nand get ourselves a copy of Greed Island ! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.48,0:06:16.10,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}王！　それでは こちらも　ご賞味ください！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.48,0:06:16.10,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:47.00,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}細胞を液体に変えて…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:47.00,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I couldn't help it! Only the risky sites are profitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.98,0:06:52.98,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}くっ…　考えたな　ユピー
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.98,0:06:52.98,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It isn't working...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.99,0:06:59.53,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}おぉ…　おぉ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.99,0:06:59.53,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Now, show me what you've brought.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.53,0:07:03.50,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}おおお…。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.53,0:07:03.50,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The hair of the famous actress Sara, and a DNA test to validate authenticity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.50,0:07:06.50,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}おぉ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.50,0:07:06.50,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The right arm of an Egyptian mummy, \Ntaken directly from a pyramid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.50,0:07:10.49,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}おぉ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.50,0:07:10.49,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The scaly skin of an ichthyosis patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.01,0:07:22.10,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}なんと力強く濃厚な…。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.01,0:07:22.10,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Okay, all four of you are hired. I'm Dalzollene, the head bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.10,0:07:26.50,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}天界から 降り落ちたとしか思えぬ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.10,0:07:26.50,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's a pleasure. I'll need you to start working immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.50,0:07:33.99,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まさに　天使の滴！ あぁ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.50,0:07:33.99,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Your mission is to escort the boss \Nto a Yorknew City hotel room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.98,0:07:43.57,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}おぉ！　おぉ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.98,0:07:43.57,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The trip between airport and hotel takes approximately ninety minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.57,0:07:45.49,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あぁ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.57,0:07:45.49,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}A special car has been prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.49,0:07:49.49,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}王！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.49,0:07:49.49,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You four will provide the \Nouter ring of security. Any questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.01,0:07:53.51,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}くっ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.01,0:07:53.51,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Do you know who might \Nbe targeting the boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.02,0:08:04.49,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}共に極上の一品と断ずるに
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.02,0:08:04.49,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The boss is an important \Nfigure in the underworld. There are plenty of people with \Nreasons to hold a grudge.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.49,0:08:07.50,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}迷いの余地は皆無。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.49,0:08:07.50,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Let me rephrase since you \Ndidn't understand the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:11.52,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あっ！ あぁ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:11.52,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Regardless of grudges, do you know
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.52,0:08:15.50,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}足りぬ…　もっとだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.52,0:08:15.50,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}anyone who might actually\Ncommit to an attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.50,0:08:18.00,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}両方とも…。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.50,0:08:18.00,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If we can identify a few candidates, we'll know \Ntheir motives, styles, and circumstances, and we can prepare accordingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.52,0:08:24.52,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ありったけ…　持ってまいれ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.52,0:08:24.52,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That will facilitate protecting the boss. You said that your name is Kurapika?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.98,0:08:33.50,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うおぉ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.98,0:08:33.50,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Our job is to protect the boss, no matter who, when, \Nwhere, or how they attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.50,0:08:37.49,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あぁ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.50,0:08:37.49,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That's all you need to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.49,0:08:41.49,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}はい！ わが王！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.49,0:08:41.49,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Don't bother building a mental profile.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.01,0:08:45.01,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}喜んで！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.01,0:08:45.01,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If anything comes too close, it's hostile.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.55,0:08:51.99,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}この上ない至高 極上の喜び
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.55,0:08:51.99,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'll introduce you to the boss. Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.00,0:09:22.99,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}これは何だ!? この気持ちは!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.00,0:09:22.99,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He ignored my advice, and let himself be deceived \Nby false information, placing not only the other bodyguards, \Nbut the boss in danger as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.59,0:09:30.98,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}これからは　余を
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.59,0:09:30.98,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So he was punished. You are replacing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.98,0:09:33.98,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「メルエム」と呼ぶがいい。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.98,0:09:33.98,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.49,0:09:44.01,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それこそ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.49,0:09:44.01,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Boss, I've brought the new bodyguards.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.01,0:09:49.01,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}母より賜りし　余の名前。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.01,0:09:49.01,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Please enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.52,0:10:35.99,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}絶対的存在の死と再生に際し さらに　自身を 王と共有することによって
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.52,0:10:35.99,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No kidding... They called her an important \Nfigure in the underworld, so I was expecting someone intimidating, but she turned out to be a cute little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.02,0:11:33.09,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}以前の王より明らかに！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.02,0:11:33.09,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You guys are going with us, too? Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.09,0:11:36.98,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}我々の肉体が お役に立ったのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.09,0:11:36.98,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Haven't seen your faces in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.98,0:11:40.50,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そして　王の一部に
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.98,0:11:40.50,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm here, chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.50,0:11:44.48,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何という光栄！ 何という至福！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.50,0:11:44.48,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What's our target this time? Give us our orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.99,0:11:51.99,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}王の意識まで 共有しているかのよう！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.99,0:11:51.99,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Feitan's group won't arrive until evening. We'll wait until everyone's here. You have no patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.48,0:11:59.48,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}しかし…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.48,0:11:59.48,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Oh? Is that Shizuku?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.47,0:12:02.97,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}だからこそ分かる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.47,0:12:02.97,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.49,0:12:06.49,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}王は　今…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.49,0:12:06.49,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Has the other new addition arrived yet? No idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.00,0:12:40.00,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}先ほどの料理も　お望みとあれば まだ　ございます。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.00,0:12:40.00,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This is for September.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.97,0:12:48.00,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あと数分で 私の分身も　ここに来る 料理…。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.97,0:12:48.00,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Huh? So many? Yeah, Rotfelli-sama and Trinc-sama \Nwould like their fortunes told.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.00,0:12:50.00,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そうか…。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.00,0:12:50.00,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That just sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.50,0:12:55.50,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あの味は現実か。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.50,0:12:55.50,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I told you to stop increasing my workload. I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.48,0:13:03.48,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まばゆい光の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.48,0:13:03.48,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And what's Daddy doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.48,0:13:06.98,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何者かが余の名前を呼んだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.48,0:13:06.98,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He had to attend a meeting. He's probably off playing golf or hunting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.48,0:13:10.98,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「メルエム」と。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.48,0:13:10.98,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Daddy? This is Neon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.98,0:13:25.50,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}なぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.98,0:13:25.50,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Fine, you have to keep your word.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.50,0:13:28.50,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}余が　ここにいるのか…。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.50,0:13:28.50,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If you break another promise, I'll quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.47,0:13:32.99,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}思い出せぬ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.47,0:13:32.99,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yay! I get another piece of treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.99,0:13:34.99,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.99,0:13:34.99,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}A sweet deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.53,0:13:41.58,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}メルエム様…。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.53,0:13:41.58,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Since that's settled, I'll get this over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.99,0:13:53.49,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}気分は悪くない。 いや…　むしろ 全身に力が　みなぎっている。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.99,0:13:53.49,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Angelic Auto Writing\NLovely Ghostwriter
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.00,0:14:19.51,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}我々の分身を 偵察に出しております。 敵の残党を捜し出し 始末するため…。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.00,0:14:19.51,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I hear she's an incredible diviner. Thanks to her father's connections, she's made clients of some very \Nimportant people in the underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.51,0:14:23.04,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うっ！ あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.51,0:14:23.04,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No, it's the other way around. Other way around?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.04,0:14:28.98,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}たとえ　余をおもんぱかってのこと だとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.04,0:14:28.98,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'd say that the father has used \Nhis daughter to increase his standing in the underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.98,0:14:32.97,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}余に対する偽りは　背信と心得よ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.98,0:14:32.97,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That's why he is frightened of losing her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.97,0:14:36.97,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}もう　二度は言わぬぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.97,0:14:36.97,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Afraid that his enemies might strike back at his daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.49,0:14:45.55,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}余は　食ったのだな？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.49,0:14:45.55,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Okay, all done. Here. Excellent work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:50.49,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お主達を。 我々が 差し出したのでございます！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:50.49,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Say, tomorrow's auction starts at night, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.49,0:14:54.99,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}差し出がましいまねとは知りつつ 全て我々の一存！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.49,0:14:54.99,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I want to do some shopping beforehand. Very well, I shall accompany you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.99,0:15:12.48,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}私とユピーの　もともとの姿は 覚えておいでのご様子。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.99,0:15:12.48,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}How many years has it been
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.48,0:15:17.48,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ならば　我々が初めて 王にお仕えした日のことは？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.48,0:15:17.48,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}since all thirteen Troupe members gathered, Feitan? Three years, two months. However, two members have since changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.50,0:15:24.50,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}分からぬ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.50,0:15:24.50,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}#4 and #8 are now different people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.55,0:15:29.98,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お主達が護衛軍 プフとユピーであることは
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.55,0:15:29.98,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Machi, will #4, Hisoka, actually show up today?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.98,0:15:32.50,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}見た瞬間に認識できた。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.98,0:15:32.50,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.50,0:15:37.00,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}いや…　正確には 思い出したというべきか。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.50,0:15:37.00,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Don't ask me. Wasn't he your responsibility? I was only supposed to tell him to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.00,0:15:41.97,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}だが　前後の経緯となると 記憶がない。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.00,0:15:41.97,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I don't like Hisoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.97,0:15:45.01,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}メルエム様。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.97,0:15:45.01,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Why does the chief let \Nhim do as he pleases? Because he has skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.01,0:15:47.56,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}恐らく　爆発の衝撃による
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.01,0:15:47.56,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Skills, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.56,0:15:50.50,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}一時的な 記憶障害でございましょう。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.56,0:15:50.50,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}His Bungee Gum is quite impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.50,0:15:53.50,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}爆発…。 はい。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.50,0:15:53.50,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It would be difficult to counter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.00,0:15:58.47,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}王は 自ら敵と　１対１の決闘に臨み
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.00,0:15:58.47,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What's your point? Are you claiming that the \Nchief is afraid of Hisoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.47,0:16:00.99,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ここへ来ました。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.47,0:16:00.99,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I won't let that statement stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.99,0:16:07.48,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}しかし　卑劣な人間どもは 強力な爆弾という 汚い手段でもって
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.99,0:16:07.48,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That's not what I meant. You're all being too generous. \NHe's nothing special.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.48,0:16:11.98,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}王の誠意に 裏切りで応えたのです！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.48,0:16:11.98,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Talk is cheap, as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.49,0:16:23.01,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そう　余は
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.49,0:16:23.01,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Nobunaga, this is what happens when I \Nkeep quiet and let you yap.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.01,0:16:27.48,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}１対１で戦っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.01,0:16:27.48,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You were talking as much as I was, Franklin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.48,0:16:31.00,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}王の生命力　運命力を もってすれば
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.48,0:16:31.00,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And so it begins. Ignore them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.00,0:16:35.98,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}人間ごときの兵器で致命傷を 受ける道理はございません。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.00,0:16:35.98,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They're just playing around again. Anyway, why is the chief \Ncalling everyone together?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.98,0:16:40.48,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}しかし　あまりに 痛ましいお姿を見るに堪えず
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.98,0:16:40.48,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We're thieves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.48,0:16:43.53,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}叱責を受けるのは承知の上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.48,0:16:43.53,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}There's something he wants us to steal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.53,0:16:47.03,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}微力ながら 回復の一助となった次第。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.53,0:16:47.03,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Well, I know that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.47,0:16:52.99,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}もともと 我々の体は余す所なく
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.47,0:16:52.99,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yes, we've arrived at the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.99,0:16:56.50,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}王　ご自身が所有されるもの。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.99,0:16:56.50,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}However, one of the lady's \Nfortunes concerned me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.50,0:17:01.00,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}我々は　王にお返しした だけのことでございます。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.50,0:17:01.00,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}"An underground chamber \Nwhere everything costs extra. That is where you will sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.97,0:17:05.47,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}宮殿へ戻りましょう。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.97,0:17:05.47,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Never descend stairs that \Nyou didn't first ascend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.06,0:17:11.06,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それが 記憶回復の早道にございます。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.06,0:17:11.06,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Do not compete with others at numbers." There were three other poems \Nthat begin with this verse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.00,0:17:15.00,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}これは…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.00,0:17:15.00,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Meaning that all four clients \Nreceived the same fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.98,0:17:19.99,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}千載一遇の
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.98,0:17:19.99,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The only thing connecting them
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.99,0:17:21.99,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}チャンス！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.99,0:17:21.99,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}is that they will be attending the \Nunderground auction this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.51,0:17:31.08,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ひと足先に宮殿へ戻り… あれを始末する
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.51,0:17:31.08,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So the fortune is saying that \Ntheir lives are at risk, should they participate?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.08,0:17:35.50,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}今ならば 王に　あれの記憶はない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.08,0:17:35.50,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm assuming that "sleep" is a metaphor for succumbing to illness or death.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.50,0:17:42.47,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}今ならば あれの存在を消してしまえば 思い出す機会もなくなる理屈！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.50,0:17:42.47,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I understand. I will pass the fortunes on to the clients. One more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.98,0:17:49.52,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}やることは ピトーの説得？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.98,0:17:49.52,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The lady never remembers \Nthe fortunes she's told, and she cannot tell her own fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.52,0:17:55.00,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}邪魔な人間どもの排除？ いや！　まず…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.52,0:17:55.00,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Does it make sense to let her \Nparticipate in the auction? No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.00,0:17:58.01,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何よりも…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.00,0:17:58.01,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Bring her back immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.01,0:18:01.48,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あれの息の根を止める
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.01,0:18:01.48,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}However, I will need a proper \Nexplanation, or she'll never listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.50,0:18:08.00,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}殺ってしまえば 後は　どうとでもなるのです
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.50,0:18:08.00,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If she throws a tantrum, \Nwe won't be able to stop her. In any case, don't take her \Nto the auction site.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.02,0:18:11.59,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}王が　これから 宮殿に向かうとして
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.02,0:18:11.59,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Send some bodyguards to place bids.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.59,0:18:14.59,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}全力で走っても ２０分は　かかる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.59,0:18:14.59,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.49,0:18:33.04,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}おぉ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.49,0:18:33.04,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The sun's about to rise. Damn Hisoka...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.04,0:18:38.54,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}生まれた時から　我が身の 一部だったかのような自然さ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.04,0:18:38.54,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Next time I see him, I'll tear him apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.50,0:18:42.00,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}すぐにでも飛べる。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.50,0:18:42.00,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Oh, dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.47,0:18:49.97,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あぁ…！ あっ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.47,0:18:49.97,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}How very scary. Hisoka, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.49,0:18:53.50,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}宮殿はどっちだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.49,0:18:53.50,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You're late. Man, I thought you weren't going to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.50,0:18:58.50,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}北です　今の王ならば　急げば １５分ほどで着きましょう！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.50,0:18:58.50,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You asked me to come...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.98,0:19:08.98,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ある。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.98,0:19:08.98,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Chief, everyone's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.97,0:19:43.48,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}速い！ もたもたしてたら追い付かれる １５分？ いや　このスピードなら
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.97,0:19:43.48,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}There will be multiple copies of the \Nmost expensive game ever for sale. Wouldn't it be logical to take \Nprecious metals and gemstones? Everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.48,0:19:50.05,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}５分で着いてしまう 猶予は長くて２３分 急げ！　私の分身！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.48,0:19:50.05,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We're taking everything \Nthat's up for auction.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.49,0:19:59.98,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}これは賭けだ 宮殿の前に整然と並ぶ 数百万の人の群れを見れば
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.49,0:19:59.98,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Are you serious, chief? The underground auction is run by \Ngangs from across the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.98,0:20:02.98,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}王は　きっと思い出してくださる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.98,0:20:02.98,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If we do that, we'll be making \Nenemies of them all...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.98,0:20:08.98,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}生物統一こそ 唯一無二の目的だと！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.98,0:20:08.98,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Are you frightened, Uvogin? I'm thrilled!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.47,0:20:15.98,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あの小娘さえ 目に入らなければ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.47,0:20:15.98,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm shaking with excitement... Give us the command, chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.98,0:20:18.50,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}護衛軍として！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.98,0:20:18.50,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.98,0:20:26.48,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}消去する！ 下賤な　ヒトの娘など！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.98,0:20:26.48,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You have my permission... Kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.00,0:20:39.97,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「ハコワレ」！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.00,0:20:39.97,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Good work. I have your next assignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.00,0:21:01.50,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}繭になる前に。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.00,0:21:01.50,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Complete with DNA validation. And...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.03,0:21:09.53,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}どこにいても 私には手に取るように見える。
